    Enclosing interface:
    TypeDescription.Generic

    public static interface TypeDescription.Generic.AnnotationReader
    An annotation reader is responsible for lazily evaluting type annotations if this language feature is available on the current JVM.

      static class  TypeDescription.Generic.AnnotationReader.Delegator

      static interface  TypeDescription.Generic.AnnotationReader.Dispatcher
      A dispatcher that represents the type annotation API via reflective calls if the language feature is available on the current JVM.

      A chained annotation reader for reading a component type.
